data.title: Nobel Prize Winners by Category
data.meta_description: Nobel Prize Winners by Category - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document lists Nobel Prize winners in chemistry from 1901 to 1995, including their year, name, country, and achievement. It provides information on over 150 individuals who were awarded the Nobel Prize in Chemistry for their pioneering work in areas such as chemical dynamics, organic synthesis, photochemistry, spectroscopy, and molecular biology.
